<section xml:id="intro">

<info><title>Introduction</title></info>

<para>
Some improvised, non-Alcoholic, <link
xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cocktail">cocktails</link> (= mixes
of several drinks or ingredients) I came up with.
</para>

<caution xml:id="non-professionality-warning">

<info>
<title>Note: I am not a professional</title>
</info>

<para>
I am not a qualified bartender. Moreover, it is possible that these cocktails
will trigger some allergies. Use at your own risk.
</para>

</caution>

</section>

<section xml:id="cocktails-list">

<info>
<title>Cocktails’ list</title>
</info>

<section xml:id="orange-juice-with-sprite">

<info>
<title>Fresh Orange Juice with Sprite or 7-Up</title>
</info>

<orderedlist>

<listitem>
<para>
<link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orange_juice">Fresh Orange Juice</link> - e.g <link xlink:href="https://www.primor.co.il/">Primor</link>.
</para>
</listitem>

<listitem>
<para>
<link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sprite_(drink)">Sprite</link>,
<link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/7_Up">7 Up</link> or
a different lemon-lime-flavoured drink.
</para>
</listitem>

</orderedlist>

<para>
Tastes somewhat like <link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fanta">Orange Fanta</link> or <link xlink:href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mirinda">Orange Mirinda</link>, only somewhat more lively.
</para>

</section>

<section xml:id="apple-juice-with-sprite">

<info>
<title>Fresh Apple Juice with Sprite or 7-Up</title>
</info>

<para>
Also works well.
</para>

</section>

<section xml:id="water-with-a-touch-of-orange-juice">

<info>
<title>Water with a touch of orange juice</title>
</info>

<para>
Water with a touch of orange juice can often be drinked instead of
water with some lemon extract.
</para>

